{"tid":166772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩係地鐵兇鳩個廢老打尖 #yup#","createTime":"2017-03-22T11:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T14:38:33.000Z","uid":2771,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4fb1b520582615b84165c93ffc449412b7b55be","tid":166772,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:24:29.000Z","msg":"本身10幾個人係門右邊排三行打斜咁等上車<br />\n我就排最左果行隊尾<br />\n跟住有個廢老阿婆失驚無神企左係我左手邊同我平排<br />\n我已經覺得有啲唔對路 就打醒十二分精神睇佢想點<br />\n到班車就嚟到站嘅時候我feel到佢有啲小動作<br />\n於是向左踏前半步 諗住封佢去路<br />\n但佢無懼旁人視線 直接兜去玻璃門前<br />\n諗住搶頭位上車<br />\n係開門嘅一剎那<br />\n我大聲喝佢一句<br />\n「喂阿姐，識唔識排隊啊？！」<br />\n佢當堂震左震 然後下意識咁應<br />\n「比你行先囉！洗唔洗咁惡呀？！」<br />\n然後就死死氣行埋一邊比人上車先<br />\n仲要口噏噏咁唔知講咩<br />\n跟著上車之後聽到車上嘅人都贊同我嘅做法<br />\n「打尖就咪咁惡啦」<br />\n跟著佢係下個站就頂唔順落左車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1d34c8807cc212aec51af59680fb901220ca7c","tid":166772,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:24:59.000Z","msg":"天地有正氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c234aec66200e852035cff789cb79f12ec510c","tid":166772,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b1f57b8acbf57aad268a4483d692b89282b3a75","tid":166772,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b8c9dc47518effcd161aedb455936f2e9112fe","tid":166772,"uid":2771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f6de0faa5a42114ffd961df38677935e3e92d4","tid":166772,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:32:42.000Z","msg":"咁都拎黎打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"